1. Grab two slices of bread and place them on a plate
    1a. The type of bread doesn't matter
    1b. White bread is preferred
2. Grab peanut butter and jelly and place on counter
    2a. Crunchy PB is preferred
    2b. Open up both jars
3. Grab a knife (or two)
4. Scoop peanut butter with knife onto one piece of bread and spread
5. Repeat step 4 with jelly on other slice
6. Place jelly slice of bread onto peanut butter slice to marry the pb&j
7. Cut sandwich in half
8. Enjoy!